{
  "texts": [
    "Ai2 ScholarQA collects all search results before generation and does not perform iterative searches.",
    "To create synthetic data with iterative searches, we transformed the data provided in the Ai2 ScholarQA traces.",
    "Each trace consists of retrieved results, CoT planning steps, and an answer with citations.",
    "We used GPT-4.1 to create a sub-query for each section in the Ai2 ScholarQA.",
    "The sub-query was generated conditioned on the section text and retrieved papers cited in the section."
  ]
}